# Library Management System - Web API (.NET 8)

## Overview
This project is a basic Library Management System built using ASP.NET Core Web API (.NET 8).  
It demonstrates clean architecture, object-oriented design principles, and RESTful API best practices.

The system allows:
- Managing books and members
- Borrowing and returning books
- Tracking loan records

This project is implemented as part of a technical assessment.

---

## Tech Stack
- .NET 8 (LTS)
- ASP.NET Core Web API
- Entity Framework Core
- SQL Server
- Swagger (OpenAPI)

---

